{"tid":567101,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"新特蘭班主：願意以低於奧巴美揚既價錢出售球會","createTime":"2018-02-20T14:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T19:34:56.000Z","uid":11270,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9a7a34b4cfddb865f01a3c191852931a6408259f","tid":567101,"uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:17:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/beleaguered-sunderland-put-up-sale-12053053\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Fnews%2Fbeleaguered-sunderland-put-up-sale-12053053&d=LG5iZRcf1akFTiRMjndvrQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=35618a11\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/beleaguered-sunderland-put-up-sale-12053053</a><br />\n<br />\nCrisis club Sunderland are up for sale for &pound;50million.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Manager Chris Coleman admitted on Monday that owner Ellis Short has fallen out of love with football, and appealed for a new tycoon to take charge.<br />\n</span><br />\nYears of bad decisions and poor form on the pitch has left the Wearsiders facing consecutive relegations.<br />\n<br />\nMirrorSport has been told that at one point, while they were in the Premier League, Sunderland <br />\nwere GIVING AWAY 9,000 tickets per game for<br />\n free.<br />\n<br />\nCurrent MD Martin Bain has scrapped that drain on income, but he also inherited several bad deals, a huge wage bill and spent 18 months cleaning it all up ready for a sale.<br />\n<br />\nUS-based billionaire Short wants out and has effectively handed over the keys to Bain.<br />\n<br />\nA source said: &ldquo;The club has very good infrastructure and nothing hiding under the bonnet now. The club needs a buyer.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">That &pound;50m pricetag is less than Arsenal spent on a single player last month &mdash; &pound;56m striker Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang.</span><br />\n<br />\nBain became the &ldquo;frontman&rdquo; for crowd abuse during the weekend defeat by Brentford but has had to slash Short&rsquo;s subsidy, which at one point ran at &pound;25m a year, and has little leeway to invest in players.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Sunderland now have a &pound;35m wage bill and have another season with a &pound;35m parachute payment from the Premier League.</span><br />\n<br />\nOne interested German buyer failed to prove they were serious, but the hunt is one for another."},{"pid":"79f728efd6210462b692115697a54a540bfdb53d","tid":567101,"uid":884,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:20:12.000Z","msg":"依隊垃圾解散未"},{"pid":"93ab8df660cd29cd63bdf04cee6ebeace69e00df","tid":567101,"uid":11270,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:20:55.000Z","msg":"剩係highlight比較好睇果幾段算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n50m其實以而家既市場真係唔算d咩錢，唔止阿狗，連非big 6既拖肥都有能力掉5千萬出黎買施格臣<br />\n<br />\n再加上今季同下季新特蘭都仲有得拎降落傘基金<br />\n<br />\n中資平平地真心玩得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n（早兩年av降班又係以60-80m賣咗比中資，而家爭緊升班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"017715888d3d3a27c9a0facc1709e362ad23dd41","tid":567101,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"最後一年英超窮撚到冬季0買人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f9587d3c26c90d78424d1fc594a5e42aacf668","tid":567101,"uid":11270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"017715888d3d3a27c9a0facc1709e362ad23dd41","tid":567101,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"最後一年英超窮撚到冬季0買人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"有，椰子係拖肥執咗奧維度同喼神<br />\n呢兩個都要比錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}