ssets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T18:40:51.000Z","msg":"蓋狗要炒幾多場場紙先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T18:47:14.000Z","msg":"一兩個月就有啦"},{"pid":"cc97221d5eb0e9fa1a46178639a1d299b399a80a","tid":567101,"uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T05:04:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/true-price-buying-sunderland-would-14320554\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chroniclelive.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Ffootball-news%2Ftrue-price-buying-sunderland-would-14320554&d=LG5iZRcf1akFTiRMjndvrQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ebd0c325\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/true-price-buying-sunderland-would-14320554</a><br />\n<br />\nHowever, the bank debt would still exist and either have to be taken on by a new owner or paid off - making the overall price of purchasing the club debt-free a lot higher than &pound;50m.<br />\n<br />\nExactly how much more is not known because it is not clear how high the club&rsquo;s debt stands at currently.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The most recent club accounts were released in July 2016 and showed the club&rsquo;s overall debt to be at &pound;136.6m - &pound;67.9m of which was owed to the bank</span>. What&rsquo;s more, they were paying &pound;8.1m a year in interest on the debt divided between the bank and Short.<br />\n<br />\n原來仲有成億三既街數要咩上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隨時免費送出去都無人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nStill, with the debt taken into account, the price is going to look steep. <span style=\"color: red;\">For comparison, in the summer of 2016 Dr Tony Xia bought Aston Villa for just &pound;76m (&pound;20m bank overdraft included).</span><br />\n<br />\n隻榜尾黑貓計埋街數都仲貴人地av成倍有多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}